ning ceremony\", \"from\": 1046, \"to\": 1066}, {\"ngram\": \"the hockey\", \"from\": 1079, \"to\": 1089}, {\"ngram\": \"gymnastics\", \"from\": 1091, \"to\": 1101}, {\"ngram\": \"[rugby] sevens game\", \"from\": 1106, \"to\": 1125}]}, {\"sentence\": \"\\\"I opened Ekhaya village and watched the rest of the Olympic Games on TV.\", \"from\": 1128, \"to\": 1201, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"Ekhaya village\", \"from\": 1138, \"to\": 1152}, {\"ngram\": \"the rest\", \"from\": 1165, \"to\": 1173}, {\"ngram\": \"the Olympic Games\", \"from\": 1177, \"to\": 1194}, {\"ngram\": \"TV\", \"from\": 1198, \"to\": 1200}]}, {\"sentence\": \"What joyride?\\\"\", \"from\": 1202, \"to\": 1216, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"What joyride\", \"from\": 1202, \"to\": 1214}]}, {\"sentence\": \"McKenzie said in a post on X, formerly known as Twitter.\", \"from\": 1217, \"to\": 1273, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 1265, \"end\": 1272, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Twitter\", \"score\": 1.0, \"rank\": 1.7719496217890764e-15, \"text\": \"Twitter\", \"types\": [\"Q386724\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Twitter\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Twitter\"}], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"McKenzie\", \"from\": 1217, \"to\": 1225}, {\"ngram\": \"a post\", \"from\": 1234, \"to\": 1240}, {\"ngram\": \"X\", \"from\": 1244, \"to\": 1245}]}, {\"sentence\": \"\\\"I left the day the Olympics started, I went for government meetings with ministers of other countries.\", \"from\": 1275, \"to\": 1378, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"the day\", \"from\": 1283, \"to\": 1290}, {\"ngram\": \"the Olympics\", \"from\": 1291, \"to\": 1303}, {\"ngram\": \"government meetings\", \"from\": 1324, \"to\": 1343}, {\"ngram\": \"ministers\", \"from\": 1349, \"to\": 1358}, {\"ngram\": \"other countries\", \"from\": 1362, \"to\": 1377}]}, {\"sentence\": \"I did not attend the Olympics, only the opening, and I came back to work.\", \"from\": 1379, \"to\": 1452, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"the Olympics\", \"from\": 1396, \"to\": 1408}, {\"ngram\": \"only the opening\", \"from\": 1410, \"to\": 1426}, {\"ngram\": \"work\", \"from\": 1447, \"to\": 1451}]}, {\"sentence\": \"ALSO READ:'F1 is definitely coming to SA,' says Gayton McKenzie [VIDEO] \\\"I could have stayed [longer] but wanted to get to know my new portfolio.\", \"from\": 1454, \"to\": 1600, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 1492, \"end\": 1494, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/South_Africa\", \"score\": 1.0, \"rank\": 3.2649680854085943e-15, \"text\": \"SA\", \"types\": [\"Q6256\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/South_Africa\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/South_Africa\"}, {\"begin\": 1502, \"end\": 1517, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Gayton_McKenzie\", \"score\": 1.0, \"rank\": 0.0, \"text\": \"Gayton McKenzie\", \"types\": [], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Gayton_McKenzie\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Gayton_McKenzie\"}], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"READ:'F1\", \"from\": 1459, \"to\": 1467}, {\"ngram\": \"[VIDEO\", \"from\": 1518, \"to\": 1524}, {\"ngram\": \"my new portfolio\", \"from\": 1582, \"to\": 1598}]}, {\"sentence\": \"Stop lying to people,\\\" the minister added.\", \"from\": 1601, \"to\": 1643, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"people\", \"from\": 1615, \"to\": 1621}, {\"ngram\": \"the minister\", \"from\": 1624, \"to\": 1636}]}, {\"sentence\": \"Eight officials had accompanied McKenzie to Paris.\", \"from\": 1645, \"to\": 1695, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 1689, \"end\": 1694, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Paris\", \"score\": 0.9999999993169695, \"rank\": 6.831941256640166e-10, \"text\": \"Paris\", \"types\": [\"Q486972\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Paris\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Paris\"}], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"Eight officials\", \"from\": 1645, \"to\": 1660}, {\"ngram\": \"McKenzie\", \"from\": 1677, \"to\": 1685}]}, {\"sentence\": \"The budget approved for officials to attend the Olympics was R1,805,355, according to the minister.\", \"from\": 1697, \"to\": 1796, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"The budget\", \"from\": 1697, \"to\": 1707}, {\"ngram\": \"officials\", \"from\": 1721, \"to\": 1730}, {\"ngram\": \"the Olympics\", \"from\": 1741, \"to\": 1753}, {\"ngram\": \"the minister\", \"from\": 1783, \"to\": 1795}]}, {\"sentence\": \"\\\"No other officials from DSAC travelled to the Olympics,\\\" McKenzie said in anotherparliamentary reply.\", \"from\": 1798, \"to\": 1900, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"No other officials\", \"from\": 1799, \"to\": 1817}, {\"ngram\": \"DSAC\", \"from\": 1823, \"to\": 1827}, {\"ngram\": \"the Olympics\", \"from\": 1841, \"to\": 1853}, {\"ngram\": \"McKenzie\", \"from\": 1856, \"to\": 1864}, {\"ngram\": \"anotherparliamentary reply\", \"from\": 1873, \"to\": 1899}]}, {\"sentence\": \"I attended six meetings in Paris before the start of the Olympics, i went to the athletic villa to greet our athletes, I attended opening ceremony and watch the hockey, gymnastic & sevens game, I opened Ekhaya village & watched the rest of the Olympic Games on TV.\", \"from\": 1902, \"to\": 2166, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 1929, \"end\": 1934, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Paris\", \"score\": 0.9999999993169695, \"rank\": 6.831941256640166e-10, \"text\": \"Paris\", \"types\": [\"Q486972\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Paris\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Paris\"}], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"six meetings\", \"from\": 1913, \"to\": 1925}, {\"ngram\": \"the start\", \"from\": 1942, \"to\": 1951}, {\"ngram\": \"the Olympics\", \"from\": 1955, \"to\": 1967}, {\"ngram\": \"the athletic villa\", \"from\": 1979, \"to\": 1997}, {\"ngram\": \"our athletes\", \"from\": 2007, \"to\": 2019}, {\"ngram\": \"opening ceremony\", \"from\": 2