m\": \"R30,000\", \"from\": 3020, \"to\": 3027}]}, {\"sentence\": \"These flights werepaidfor by the South African Sports Confederation and Olympic Committee (SASCOC).\", \"from\": 3030, \"to\": 3129, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"These flights werepaidfor\", \"from\": 3030, \"to\": 3055}, {\"ngram\": \"the South African Sports Confederation\", \"from\": 3059, \"to\": 3097}, {\"ngram\": \"Olympic Committee\", \"from\": 3102, \"to\": 3119}, {\"ngram\": \"SASCOC\", \"from\": 3121, \"to\": 3127}]}, {\"sentence\": \"Following his appointment to Cabinet, McKenzie announced he would put an end to public funding forsuperfans like Mama Joy Chauke and Botha Msila, who frequently travelled internationally to support South African teams.\", \"from\": 3131, \"to\": 3349, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 3160, \"end\": 3167, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Cabinet_of_the_United_Kingdom\", \"score\": 0.9990433459724459, \"rank\": 0.00045014905307737616, \"text\": \"Cabinet\", \"types\": [\"Q43229\", \"Q327333\", \"Q24229398\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Cabinet_of_the_United_Kingdom\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Cabinet_of_the_United_Kingdom\"}, {\"begin\": 3249, \"end\": 3252, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Joy\", \"score\": 0.9774514824525079, \"rank\": 0.02306868213109748, \"text\": \"Joy\", \"types\": [], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Joy\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Joy\"}, {\"begin\": 3253, \"end\": 3259, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Chauke\", \"score\": 0.9999999996912265, \"rank\": 0.0, \"text\": \"Chauke\", \"types\": [\"Q486972\", \"Q3957\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Chauke\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Chauke\"}, {\"begin\": 3264, \"end\": 3269, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/P._W._Botha\", \"score\": 0.5956563000808731, \"rank\": 0.6788204873588382, \"text\": \"Botha\", \"types\": [\"Q82955\", \"Q729\", \"Q5\", \"Q215627\", \"Q19088\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/P._W._Botha\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/P._W._Botha\"}, {\"begin\": 3270, \"end\": 3275, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/M'Sila_Province\", \"score\": 0.9999999999831743, \"rank\": 1.473344779532717e-11, \"text\": \"Msila\", \"types\": [\"Q486972\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/M'Sila_Province\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/M'Sila_Province\"}], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"his appointment\", \"from\": 3141, \"to\": 3156}, {\"ngram\": \"McKenzie\", \"from\": 3169, \"to\": 3177}, {\"ngram\": \"an end\", \"from\": 3201, \"to\": 3207}, {\"ngram\": \"public funding forsuperfans\", \"from\": 3211, \"to\": 3238}, {\"ngram\": \"South African teams\", \"from\": 3329, \"to\": 3348}]}, {\"sentence\": \"He cited cost-cutting as the primary reason for this decision.\", \"from\": 3351, \"to\": 3413, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"cost-cutting\", \"from\": 3360, \"to\": 3372}, {\"ngram\": \"the primary reason\", \"from\": 3376, \"to\": 3394}, {\"ngram\": \"this decision\", \"from\": 3399, \"to\": 3412}]}, {\"sentence\": \"I have stopped all trips for super fans, we have athletes & artist who are struggling to raise money to attend sporting events and exhibitions, how do we justify paying for fans?\", \"from\": 3415, \"to\": 3593, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"all trips\", \"from\": 3430, \"to\": 3439}, {\"ngram\": \"super fans\", \"from\": 3444, \"to\": 3454}, {\"ngram\": \"athletes\", \"from\": 3464, \"to\": 3472}, {\"ngram\": \"artist\", \"from\": 3475, \"to\": 3481}, {\"ngram\": \"money\", \"from\": 3510, \"to\": 3515}, {\"ngram\": \"sporting events\", \"from\": 3526, \"to\": 3541}, {\"ngram\": \"exhibitions\", \"from\": 3546, \"to\": 3557}, {\"ngram\": \"fans\", \"from\": 3588, \"to\": 3592}]}, {\"sentence\": \"We shall no longer be paying for these trips and will use that money where it's needed the most.\", \"from\": 3594,